25
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,680
The bronze paperweight from the Imperial Guard has been stolen.

26
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,640
Is there any word on the thieves?

27
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,280
Commander Feng says

28
