32
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,040
Yes, sir.

33
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,160
How are you?

34
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,120
Are you hurt?

35
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,720
I heard from Brother Feng that you went to catch Qing Gui.

36
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,440
I was worried about you.

37
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,600
Xiao Wei will be here with people in no time.

38
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,000
Why aren't you resting at the Feng mansion?

39
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,600
Why did you steal this paperweight that has nothing to do with you?

40
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,640
This paperweight looks very similar to the one in my mother's study.

41
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,560
That night when Qing Gui broke into the Feng mansion,

42
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,680
it was to steal this.

43
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,480
How can you say it has nothing to do with me?

44
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,320
The dead are gone.

45
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,840
The Situ mansion is now in ruins.

46
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,640
Do you want to spend your whole life consumed by hatred?

47
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,720
I thought you understood me.

48
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,360
Yun'er,

49
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,560
let's look forward together.

50
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,400
Forget about Qing Gui.

51
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,960
Let's go to a new place

52
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,480
and build a new home together, okay?

53
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,640
If I were just Qing Dai,

54
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,040
perhaps I could run away with you.

55
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,200
But I have always been Situ Wannan's daughter.

56
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,160
All these years, I've been searching for Qing Gui.

57
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,640
Now he has finally appeared.

58
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,960
We're about to catch him.

59
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,640
I can't possibly give up now.

60
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,240
What about for me?

61
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,079
Mo Ze,

62
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,840
As long as we can catch the Blue Ghost,

63
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,560
we can avenge my mother

64
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,000
and your father.

65
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:05,600
We can uncover all the truth from back then.

66
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:07,960
Why are you asking me such questions

67
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,080
at such a crucial moment?

68
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:11,120
What if the truth isn't what you think it is?

69
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,760
Then tell me, what is the truth?

70
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,560
You can still leave now,

71
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,640
otherwise you'll have no chance once the patrol officers come in.

72
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,440
I almost forgot,

73
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,000
you're also from the patrol.

74
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,440
Since you consider me a colonel from the patrol,

75
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,680
then you must be the person we're after.

76
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,800
Hand over the paperweight now

77
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,840
and surrender.

78
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,320
I'll notify Xiao Wei immediately

79
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,480
to ensure you're treated with respect.

80
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,680
Go in and take a look.

81
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,640
If there's anything unusual,

82
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,880
report to me immediately.

83
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:05,960
Go.

84
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:09,000
We've been friends,

85
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,880
let's not ruin our relationship.

86
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,080
Although my surname is Mo,

87
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,840
I'm actually the second young master of the Feng family in the south of the city.

88
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,160
My family is well-off,

89
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,560
and I hold a salaried position in the government office.

90
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,400
Though I may not be as handsome as Pan An,

91
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,720
