92
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,920
If I catch the Blue Ghost

93
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,040
and avenge your family,

94
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,280
would you marry me?

95
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:35,480
I'm fond of you,

96
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,880
not because you resemble someone else,

97
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,159
but simply because I like you.

98
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,680
Only in long illness do you know who truly loves you,

99
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,840
